commits.message: add - some ackages to base Dockerfile

Merge pull request #827 from anaHue/master

add - some packages to base Dockerfile
fix - change class for file code icon

Merge pull request #829 from anaHue/fix_missing_icon

[Frontend/Submissions] fix - change class for file code icon
add - submission date to feedback
use strftime instead of replacing microseconds
corrected the display for submission date

Merge pull request #831 from anaHue/fix_issue_278

add - submission date to feedback

[frontend/course admin] switch course settings layout to tabs (#821)

* using tabs to simplify display

* fix tiny bug if "activate lti" is checked and then unchecked, it displays "access control type" independently of selected access control

* Hide lti tab if lti option is not activated in general tab
[frontend/course_admin] fix bad student count (#836)

[filesystems/local] use copy2 instead of copy (#840)

This keeps the file metadata (permissions, dates, ...). Fix #390
[frontend/course_admin] move tags page to settings page (#841)

[course_admin/edit_tabs] add network interface hint tooltip (#839)

Fix #798

[frontend] Moving the concept of weight into the Task Dispenser (#849)

Warning: this doesn't ensure retrocompatibilty with previous weighing system.
[task_dispenser/combinatory_test] now return a proper dispenser data (#852)
[frontend] Moving the number of stored submission into the Task Dispenser (#851)
[ci] temporarily mitigate issue with markupsafe
[frontend] Moving the concept of evaluation submission into the Task Dispenser (#854)
[doc] fix #856 : typo in hidden-until docs
[frontend] Categories managed by the Task Dispenser (#855)
